    <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="border border-surface-200 bg-white"><img src={cardImg.src} alt="" class="h-[260px] w-full object-cover" /><div class="px-4 pb-4"><div class="flex gap-4 pt-3 text-sm text-text-500"><span>12/12/2025</span><span>1232</span></div><h3 class="pt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-7">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Nam quisque egestas amet tellus</h3><p class="pt-3 leading-7 text-text-700">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Fringilla orci quis pellentesque arcu elementum pellentesque dictumst.</p></div></article>
