    <div class="grid gap-5 xl:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <details class="mb-3 bg-surface-100 px-4 py-3" open><summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-lg text-text-900 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"><span>Co the thuc hien nhung thay doi lon sau khi cong viec tu sua da bat dau khong?</span><span class="text-xl font-light">−</span></summary><p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-text-700">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Id morbi eget posuere nam vulputate a velit.</p></details>
