        <details class="mb-3 bg-surface-100 px-4 py-3"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-lg text-text-900 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"><span>Thoi gian hoan thien mot du an keo dai bao lau?</span><span class="text-xl font-light">+</span></summary></details>
        <details class="mb-3 bg-surface-100 px-4 py-3"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-lg text-text-900 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"><span>Co ho tro thiet ke theo dien tich nho khong?</span><span class="text-xl font-light">+</span></summary></details>
